# Build artifact — local devShell shellHook (flake.nix) symlinks this
# into public/ for `trunk serve` to find. CI re-renders it from
# `nix run github:pleme-io/ishou#css` per pages-deploy.yml. Tracking
# the symlink in git breaks CI (the symlink target is a /nix/store/
# path that doesn't exist on the runner, so `> public/ishou-tokens.css`
# returns Permission denied).
/public/ishou-tokens.css
